WEBVTT

00:00.078 --> 00:01.328
Previously on
"the secret circle"...

00:01.881 --> 00:04.717
My sweet Cassie,
you finding this means I'm gone,

00:04.718 --> 00:06.051
and for that I am so sorry.

00:06.119 --> 00:07.503
I didn't want you
to have this life,

00:07.587 --> 00:09.839
but destiny's not easy
to run from.

00:09.923 --> 00:11.123
Hi. I'm Diana.

00:11.174 --> 00:12.641
You seen her yet?
She got in yesterday.

00:12.726 --> 00:14.310
- We're different.
- You're different.

00:14.394 --> 00:17.930
You're a witch. You're a
full-blooded 100% witch.

00:17.981 --> 00:20.082
Here we have
real power now.

00:20.150 --> 00:21.817
A complete circle is 6.

00:21.902 --> 00:22.818
You complete
the circle.

00:22.903 --> 00:24.270
She's got the gift.

00:24.337 --> 00:26.655
You can get Cassie
to do what we need?

00:26.723 --> 00:29.141
The circle will take care
of that without even knowing it.

00:29.209 --> 00:31.827
And my mother did something to
Heather that was worse than death.

00:31.912 --> 00:33.812
She hasn't moved
in 16 years.

00:34.241 --> 00:36.542
She had to be the one
to put the spell on Heather.

00:36.627 --> 00:38.744
Wherever there are witches,
evil follows.

00:38.829 --> 00:41.030
They were trying to use
your mother's power.

00:41.081 --> 00:43.049
I tell you, she was
trying to stop.

00:43.133 --> 00:44.500
Demons!

00:44.551 --> 00:46.385
We need to know what
happened 16 years ago.

