01:05.087 --> 01:07.423
Wake up. We're late.

01:07.491 --> 01:09.609
Are you dead? Hmm?

01:14.915 --> 01:17.566
Oh.

01:17.618 --> 01:21.037
Ohh. Oh, I have
such a headache.

01:26.293 --> 01:27.293
Mmm...

01:27.377 --> 01:30.346
Ugh! Get off!

01:31.215 --> 01:32.598
What the hell?

01:32.683 --> 01:34.433
I said my head hurts.

01:34.518 --> 01:40.422
I'm sorry.
I just really don't feel well.

